title: Cheeze gives a live performance of 'Mood Indigo' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Cheeze gives a live performance of 'Mood Indigo' By KpopJoA 2 minutes ago 135 0 0 0 Google+ Indie singer Cheeze gave a casual live performance of new song "Mood Indigo." 
Starting off with a jazzy piano tune, Cheeze is presented with a tasty rainbow cake as she sings aloud. 
"Mood Indigo" is sure to brighten up the mood of listeners with its cheerfulness.
